Feature Identifies the behaviour of all features.

Class Summary
DrawableFactory Factory to produce drawable renderers.
GeoMap Class for drawing geographic maps in Processing
Line Class for representing and drawing a line feature.

Enum Summary
FeatureType Enumerates the different feature types.
 

Package org.gicentre.geomap Description

Classes for representing geographic vector maps in Processing. Can store and draw point, line and polygon objects.

The main class usable from Processing is the GeoMap class. The others support internal data structures.
